      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been garage-kept and pampered since day one, so you won't find a single scratch or dent on this beauty. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next big adventure. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
