      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the naturally aspirated S54B32 inline-six with its signature 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This specimen boasts impeccable mechanical provenance, with a documented VANOS overhaul and proactive subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis longevity. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, providing peerless tactile feedback. The exterior retains its factory luster, while the suspension geometry remains tight and responsive, free of any bushing deflection. This is a turn-key collector piece with a zero-fault diagnostic report and comprehensive service history.",
